Then this afternoon I hung out with Joseph, Kenny, and Cody...and i also stopped by tiffanys house while Joseph took a shower. Me and Kenny had one of our little bonding moments..shhh. ANYWAYS, I got home at like 11:30 and now Im on here so yeah fun day. Now Im gonna take one of those survey things if I can figure out how.

It was sooo sweet though cuz he just came in my room and kissed my head and it woke me up. Then he laid down beside me and we were just cuddling and then the next thing I knew it was like 10:30! LOL So then Joseph had to leave cuz he was going to his dads work to fix his car up from that accident. But then I went back to sleep and my mom woke me up at like 12 saying "do u want ur fries to get cold? I brought u Mc Donalds." I got up REALLY quick then cuz its McDonalds and who doesnt love McDonalds? I had chicken nuggets...YUMMY...hmmmmm that was a good meal.
   Anyways after that Chelsea came over and we hung out and then we went to the mall with her sister and I got some pretty earings. Then I.. DAMNIT MY DOGS GOT THE TOILET PAPER!!!!! Ok, lol Then I came home and Joseph came over and then we hung out and then went home and now I just got off the phone with him.. Now Im gonna go to bed cuz im sleepy and I may go to the creek tomarrow if its nice...ok goodnight
